\"  data-weight=\"0.33333333333333\" ><div id=\"panel-390-1-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_text panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"2\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" ><h3 class=\"widget-title\">СОВМЕСТИМОСТЬ</h3>			<div class=\"textwidget\"><p>Авточехлы шьются по заводским лекалам Вашего автомобиля 100% соответствие.</p>\n</div>\r\n		</div></div><div id=\"pgc-390-1-1\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell panel-grid-cell-empty\"  data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;vertical_alignment&quot;:&quot;auto&quot;}\"  data-weight=\"0.33333333333333\" ></div><div id=\"pgc-390-1-2\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"0.33333333333333\" ><div id=\"panel-390-1-2-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_text panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"3\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" ><h3 class=\"widget-title\">УДОБСТВО В ИСПОЛЬЗОВАНИИ</h3>			<div class=\"textwidget\"><p>Используя наши чехлы Вы экономите на химчистке салона. Чехлы легко снимаются и чистятся.</p>\n</div>\r\n		</div></div></div><div id=\"pg-390-2\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\" ><div id=\"pgc-390-2-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"1\" ><div id=\"panel-390-2-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_media_image panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"4\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" >[siteorigin_widget class=\"WP_Widget_Media_Image\"]<input type=\"hidden\" value=\"{&quot;instance&quot;:{&quot;attachment_id&quot;:94,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;http:\\/\\/lviv.loc\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/02\\/our-advantages-bg.png&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;full&quot;,&quot;width&quot;:522,&quot;height&quot;:636,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;link_type&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;link_url&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;image_classes&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;link_classes&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;l